import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import {createRouter, createWebHistory} from 'vue-router'
import PageSchedule from './components/page/PageSchedule.vue'
import PageEstablish from './components/page/PageEstablish.vue'
import ScreenAuthority from './components/screen/ScreenAuthority.vue'

const routers = [
    {path: "/schedule", component: PageSchedule},
    {path: "/mission", component: PageSchedule},
    {path: "/transport", component: PageSchedule},
    {path: "/advance", component: PageSchedule},
    {path: "/pay", component: PageSchedule},
    {path: "/establish", component: PageEstablish},
    {path: "/user", component: ScreenAuthority},
]

const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes: routers,
})

const app = createApp(App);

app.use(router).mount('#app')
